gw.pl.persistence.type

Interface DynamicEntityPropertyInfoReference<T extends IEntityPropertyInfo>


  • public interface DynamicEntityPropertyInfoReference<T extends IEntityPropertyInfo>
    A reference to an entity property that can only be resolved by supplying a concrete entity type. This is the reference type for entity properties defined on delegates. In the case of such properties, a separate entity property is defined per implementor of the delegate.
